ProfessionalSummary: This person built a FastAPI-based AI image generation service with Celery for asynchronous task processing and distributed job queue management. They integrated Stable Diffusion models with Transformers and Diffusers libraries for text-to-image and image-to-image generation workflows, and deployed the production system using Docker containers with load balancing and request routing infrastructure. They also implemented monitoring and observability stack to track system performance and resource utilization, and contributed to an AI platform for transforming text and sketches into artwork using generative models.
